{"tid":2200492,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇可能一隻遊戲真係整到中槍即傷(行動唔到)或者即死","createTime":"2020-09-13T04:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T01:54:22.000Z","uid":140953,"like":2,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"778d6f9625ed740b23003f7ba0f9533c6af92bcd","tid":2200492,"uid":140953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:18:07.000Z","msg":"好奇仲有冇人會玩依隻遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有d遊戲明明係玩緊既時候中幾多槍、中幾多招都冇事<br />\n但係因為劇情需要，中一槍/中一刀就死左<br />\n都覺得幾搞笑<br />\n就好似某隻大作，明明d人係槍戰都唔知中左幾多槍，但劇情一槍就掛左<br />\n又或者明明係隻遊戲度連導彈都食過，但就一刀比人殺死左...真係幾冇代入感<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw最痴線應該係隻遊戲角色死哂所有存檔刪除<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇人會挑戰架呢"},{"pid":"2ac47bb78ea41d740a764c25f0879414782922da","tid":2200492,"uid":292585,"like":45,"dislike":3,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:21:53.000Z","msg":"Escape from Tarkov<br />\n<br />\n自己查下幾hardcore<br />\n扮緊工打唔到咁多字介紹"},{"pid":"98d7ccd179efc40c48c03f96bf6f5aaca275a3bd","tid":2200492,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:28:58.000Z","msg":"已經有，詳細google樓上"},{"pid":"56b67541c6e51f57200911c457511e889f272e48","tid":2200492,"uid":61334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:41:26.000Z","msg":"call of duty 好似有得較"},{"pid":"190b433b9b4cd281013a9497878ac4d07026e905","tid":2200492,"uid":62469,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:42:30.000Z","msg":"hell let loose"},{"pid":"f1ef8e7f59f5feea6fbf96cd95b82792e6b9daff","tid":2200492,"uid":331822,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:49:54.000Z","msg":"最痴線應該係隻遊戲角色死哂所有存檔刪除<br />\n刷裝game d 天梯咪咁"},{"pid":"0fc7190c3b33f5802dc77fa84d4b2af26f5cd3d5","tid":2200492,"uid":169133,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2ac47bb78ea41d740a764c25f0879414782922da","tid":2200492,"uid":292585,"like":45,"